}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The RT3883 (with internal antennas) is assumed to be bgn only.
"WRT-893L Rev. UB" is silkscreened on the board.
The default SSIDs are assumed to be '''TRENDnet692_2.4GHz''' and '''TRENDnet692_5GHz'''. OUIs appear to include 00:14:D1 and maybe also A2:05:43.
